y tests without getting into more complex reflection-based solutions!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_017396f86f7fdf690169f8065a3a7c8194a2588f99068ab8b6\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-AZszrccYhja6NLorngC3kvfbSjG9QwGxyVgDoHbJGfCgbL-m6dfg8f919JsTrUrHrYurDlQ9kv3EDeWkU2e0w_0QV6guzKZEvTEc3GxS3mBtsD601bt7gNZgZM0iuDqI-KkQBUyJWxuGjJUYj7a7CJbaeBITeMIPc1tTGfVF5d6zxjlJNI2LMZZF3-RH1poJPTYou3XS9RufrR4Xv4G8hvNHreGwxVhv4J-Gxylhc41lz9JnAHwBO-sTFHIDdxLrUAzA9GHlHok34pAiZBLXi_87DYx9iJo2B_CDGOZAYMy1vfFR6baUafHBulNqkEQcnGRpRJdWivPgIYICpA5i6jyAPMY-2F-q07JGEpUH9xg4GvYLL7X2uarv17gPfF5Z9IOLGc4rrynGTrxxTjgPmmr6152AYrDrrUbNRJ29W_cjyROUJ68KS1Qih65SMo58Z_SV2yqajLzYGkIW6G0AYj8b-nfomjfG_KFndmCkK5rjV4aWU1790ErrNPsQaihICoJMdwIH_ti2D3vP2XUywyYFyqc7qATDf83irlIqERCoMIxaJEmin73NlLtAfYeg64_5IE1ghghK-C2ilSTFC1XHLzMKJLRK0-f0haRBQqgm7FzKoLKiV9bnZyGk5nExgYp2Wy1lrKR9Kz-is3ojdE_INJcn8YcZaA6WKV5HXWQUmk9wGAEqZzsnfjFg9XFiQYQchh0MAjn_lNuAgPiUwA11EDKjqYIss7uy1mFNa13RPF7VtAK3n_vZWMK6pE_NvCJvjYk957hgTgxty-58kKTJT05q3PaY_1_CsMzBTSP4NGAVfS4DoMVorzZUmQO9J_b-6ZJI-_zRgrsrydBjQZu--XSklc91hgPB4SFM9qa35Kle8XIvhwiJtWUuMFkJfRKONjxZkdOkTXlBzXsrddMZxuTlagThqC3Df2gie74kI1EaeoXOSe2_ECKmwi9sUofjBFHx-5uGrqC84wTNtv0OVP_WfFSZlmjJZDImT0Kk8SAMZMW-gkjE_-QnS5KgriBWhSma6-n-FYkFmUsfjIt_aq1GdO23oDls9ieCui4pG3cLxqvHuvqNYGvJTyUskrYx4g8ZE53X1ZMODMieEBIPUYLDdXdpXaMAEA7mvZI_R2hYySTEqoq2a4zXH0ERZDKxxflAHkMpTGyB389kzJCoZ6-6Zz6fn1ucXrBKNOaXB_doZzjgOQ5ZMU36Ua8zoQ5kzpWhb05k7rBcC4fvtqsHZ9j1keU4aIStGdjxThDJo37hy3pkn5LAcBXmOcqntx0Hny05BIqZPD5W7HJDYQZau1gxNoEGkBc7ykfH2MFNfbKW6KWtPAjL_fDHH0qL4vurFT1Rk6c3o8TA8R4vTXcyM0ECkH2DmmTas2VRJKp0k5XCa6WGHeBBBDIpT7cvBkODjjTptlqKh90lkjgWtCjvviIYLVkuhPsuYQPQCPGiL9pkIsOAkSpmAz8L-no7lH-vdKFsd7Cs95bOHm-o0m1AM2JUD7sQJ47VxDS4RgtIDKwe6k7cZuJe6__6GWLFa0rdFX7kzO5jGHVY27hjxC-q2WcRb_Iw4MtHp2NgZNSGQkTSFfisPtLXyNtlmyxivgYZFQXA6zOR9YLcpsMUSxx3a8AZww1ScxBL4OjUvcsIsb0hJ-mkTYcR-XVf6VYd0NG1_iHV2Xh0A1LPGRucfEbYLDSkcvhgP7tKfli32aYLyxN9OUU5vgrxWQfZcqxuyW_YB5bDM5JpgZlqwFstUXi4E7JWjchoeXb2uEV3J3Mulg4pZo-AUUQd